# Title: TAIDOOR RAT DLL Load
# Author: Florian Roth (Nextron Systems)
# Date: 2020-07-30
# Level: high
# Description: Detects specific process characteristics of Chinese TAIDOOR RAT malware load
# MITRE Tactic: Privilege Escalation
# Tags: attack.privilege-escalation, attack.execution, attack.stealth, attack.t1055.001, detection.emerging-threats
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules-emerging-threats/2020/TA/TAIDOOR-RAT/proc_creation_win_apt_taidoor.yml

CommandLine IN ("*dll,MyStart*", "*dll MyStart*") OR (CommandLine="* MyStart" CommandLine="*rundll32.exe*")